metadata.name: Starry Identity
metadata.description:
The portraits may challenge viewers to focus on other aspects of the subjects such as their clothing, posture, or surroundings, or to project their own interpretations onto the anonymous figures.

Overall, the collection and its title could invite viewers to question their assumptions about portraiture and collecting, and to consider the complex relationships between individuals, identity, and representation in art.

Become an “Irregular collector”.
